<?php
return ['messages'=>['<h4><a href="https://www.ciie.org/zbh/en/"><strong>CIIE</strong></a>5-10 November 2023</h4><p>Hall 6.2 #B1-07<br />National Exhibition and Convention Center, Shanghai</p><p><b>Opening Hours<br /></b><span style="font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); color: var(--theme-color-text); letter-spacing: 0px;">Sunday-Friday:  8:00 AM-6:00 PM</span></p>'=>'<h4><a href="https://www.ciie.org/zbh/en/"><strong>中国国际展览中心</strong></a>2023 年 11 月 5-10 日</h4><p>6.2 号馆 #B1-07<br>上海国家会展中心</p><p><b>开放时间<br></b><span style="font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); color: var(--theme-color-text); letter-spacing: 0px;">周日至周五：上午 8:00 至下午 6:00</span></p>','<iframe width="328" height="583" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S8QxWZkT5FA" title="TITANIUM | FINE JEWELLERY | EJI OFFICIAL" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>'=>'<iframe width="328" height="583" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S8QxWZkT5FA" title="钛金属 | 高级珠宝 | Eji Official" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>','<iframe width="328" height="583" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VarxO-iOI_s" title="BANGLE | D COLLECTION | GENDER NEUTRAL" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>'=>'<iframe width="328" height="583" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VarxO-iOI_s" title="手镯 | D 系列 | 不分性别" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>','<p>Another new all-gender collection plays with a mix of materials. With its smooth, contemporary aesthetic, ceramic delivers a neutral palette suitable for all. Challenging the traditional jewellery aesthetics, the unexpected materials mix highlights the distinctive designs of this monochromatic collection. Celebrating the mesmeric beauty of craftsmanship, these groundbreaking pieces feature bold designs and materials.</p><p>Don’t miss our new timeless selection for all genders.<br /><br /></p>'=>'<p>另一个全新的全性别系列采用了混合材料。陶瓷具有光滑、现代的美感，是适合所有人的中性色调。挑战传统的珠宝美学，意想不到的材料组合凸显了这一单色系列的独特设计。这些开创性的作品以大胆的设计和材质为特色，彰显了工艺的魅力。   </p><p>千万不要错过我们为所有性别设计的全新永恒之选。<br><br></p>','<p>As a pioneering B2B jeweller in Hong Kong, we are continuously excited to explore unlimited possibilities, push boundaries in techniques, materials, and expression in our jewellery creations. From minimalism to maximalism, we offer designs that keep pace with the latest jewellery trends. With us, you can always share your own ideas and enjoy our unique bespoke jewellery services. Let’s shine brighter together!</p>'=>'<p>作为香港首屈一指的 B2B 珠宝商，我们不断探索无限可能，在珠宝创作的技术、材料和表现形式上突破界限。从极简主义到极致主义，我们的设计紧跟最新的珠宝潮流。在我们这里，您可以随时分享自己的创意，享受我们独特的定制珠宝服务。让我们一起绽放璀璨光芒！   </p>','<p>Choker necklaces exude an alluring vibe. Our newest diamond choker collection features elegant minimalist styles with a contemporary twist, radiating refined elegance. At the core, a titanium cord ingeniously boosts elasticity and flexibility, allowing the slim choker to smoothly pull over the head before sitting securely yet gracefully around the neck. The durable ultra-lightweight titanium provides a long-lasting stretch and comfort, perfect for all-day wear. Accented with brilliant diamonds and coloured gemstones, this delicate new collection embraces simplicity and clean lines and focuses on craftsmanship using quality materials to make a subtle statement.</p>'=>'<p>choker 项链散发着诱人的气息。我们最新的钻石choker 系列以优雅简约的款式为特色，融入现代元素，散发出高雅的气质。项链的核心部分是一根钛金属线，它巧妙地增强了项链的弹性和柔韧性，使纤细的项链能够顺利地戴在头上，然后稳稳地、优雅地戴在脖子上。超轻钛金属经久耐用，具有持久的拉伸性和舒适性，适合全天佩戴。这个精致的新系列以璀璨的钻石和彩色宝石为点缀，线条简洁明快，注重采用优质材料的精湛工艺，彰显含蓄内敛的气质。    </p>','<p>Follow us on</p>'=>'<p>关注我们</p>','<p>Fresh off the buzzing exhibition floors of Jewellery &amp; Gem World Hong Kong 2023, the world’s premier fine jewellery B2B event, we’re thrilled to unveil our latest jewellery collections to all visitors across the world. Having debuted these stunning new designs for upcoming seasons, we’ve noticed immense intrigue around the intricate artistry and innovation of each piece. Whether you missed seeing these collections in person or want a closer glimpse, join us now as we zoom in on some breathtaking details – <strong>techniques and materials</strong> - that caught the eye of many excited attendees at the fair.</p>'=>'<p>在全球首屈一指的高级珠宝 B2B 盛会--香港国际珠宝展（Jewellery &amp; Gem World Hong Kong 2023）的热闹展场上，我们刚刚向全球所有参观者揭开了最新珠宝系列的神秘面纱。这些令人惊叹的新设计将在下一季首次亮相，我们注意到每件作品的复杂艺术性和创新性都引起了人们的极大兴趣。无论您是错过了亲眼目睹这些系列，还是想更近距离地一睹其风采，现在都请加入我们的行列，让我们放大一些令人叹为观止的细节--<strong>技术和材料</strong>--它们在展会上吸引了众多兴奋的与会者的目光。  </p>','<p>Maximalism goes gender-neutral in our D Collection featuring a distinctive, modern padlock motif design, in yellow, white, or rose gold enhanced with diamonds and gemstones. A breakthrough swivelling clasp mechanism delivers enhanced functionality of a streamlined, and elongated padlock silhouette. Unlock the secret – an innovative clasp gracefully swings open and locks in place. This feat of craftsmanship combines ingenuity with beauty, security, and comfort. Wear one on its own for a bold statement – the bolder, the better.</p>
<p>Discover our latest D Collection showcasing padlock-inspired bangles, necklaces, earrings, and rings.<br><br></p>'=>'<p>在我们的 D 系列中，"极致主义 "与 "性别中立 "并行不悖，以独特的现代挂锁图案设计为特色，黄金、白金或玫瑰金镶钻和宝石。突破性的旋转锁扣装置，为流线型的拉长挂锁轮廓提供了更强的功能性。揭开秘密--创新表扣优雅地旋转打开并锁定到位。这一工艺杰作将独创性与美观、安全和舒适融为一体。单只佩戴，大胆彰显个性--越大胆越好。    </p>
<p>探索我们最新的 D 系列产品，展示以水杉为灵感的手镯、项链、耳环和戒指。<br><br></p>','CERAMIC HITS'=>'陶瓷打击','PERFECTED TITANIUM REIGN'=>'完美的钛统治','THE PADLOCK’S SECRET'=>'锁的秘密','Upcoming exhibition'=>'即将举办的展览','editor-text-editor-10a404c'=>'<p>在我们的 D 系列中，"极致主义 "与 "性别中立 "并行不悖，以独特的现代挂锁图案设计为特色，黄金、白金或玫瑰金镶钻和宝石。突破性的旋转锁扣装置，为流线型的拉长挂锁轮廓提供了更强的功能性。揭开秘密--创新表扣优雅地旋转打开并锁定到位。这一工艺杰作将独创性与美观、安全和舒适融为一体。单只佩戴，大胆彰显个性--越大胆越好。    </p>
<p>探索我们最新的 D 系列产品，展示以水杉为灵感的手镯、项链、耳环和戒指。<br><br></p>','editor-text-editor-11fda0e'=>'<p>另一个全新的全性别系列采用了混合材料。陶瓷具有光滑、现代的美感，是适合所有人的中性色调。挑战传统的珠宝美学，意想不到的材料组合凸显了这一单色系列的独特设计。这些开创性的作品以大胆的设计和材质为特色，彰显了工艺的魅力。   </p><p>千万不要错过我们为所有性别设计的全新永恒之选。<br><br></p>','editor-text-editor-36be40b'=>'<p>作为香港首屈一指的 B2B 珠宝商，我们不断探索无限可能，在珠宝创作的技术、材料和表现形式上突破界限。从极简主义到极致主义，我们的设计紧跟最新的珠宝潮流。在我们这里，您可以随时分享自己的创意，享受我们独特的定制珠宝服务。让我们一起绽放璀璨光芒！   </p>','editor-text-editor-5e4ef88'=>'<p>choker 项链散发着诱人的气息。我们最新的钻石choker 系列以优雅简约的款式为特色，融入现代元素，散发出高雅的气质。项链的核心部分是一根钛金属线，它巧妙地增强了项链的弹性和柔韧性，使纤细的项链能够顺利地戴在头上，然后稳稳地、优雅地戴在脖子上。超轻钛金属经久耐用，具有持久的拉伸性和舒适性，适合全天佩戴。这个精致的新系列以璀璨的钻石和彩色宝石为点缀，线条简洁明快，注重采用优质材料的精湛工艺，彰显含蓄内敛的气质。    </p>','editor-text-editor-8bbbb75'=>'<p>关注我们</p>','editor-text-editor-b0640ef'=>'<h4><a href="https://www.ciie.org/zbh/en/"><strong>中国国际展览中心</strong></a>2023 年 11 月 5-10 日</h4><p>6.2 号馆 #B1-07<br>上海国家会展中心</p><p><b>开放时间<br></b><span style="font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); color: var(--theme-color-text); letter-spacing: 0px;">周日至周五：上午 8:00 至下午 6:00</span></p>','editor-text-editor-b81cfc8'=>'<p>在全球首屈一指的高级珠宝 B2B 盛会--香港国际珠宝展（Jewellery &amp; Gem World Hong Kong 2023）的热闹展场上，我们刚刚向全球所有参观者揭开了最新珠宝系列的神秘面纱。这些令人惊叹的新设计将在下一季首次亮相，我们注意到每件作品的复杂艺术性和创新性都引起了人们的极大兴趣。无论您是错过了亲眼目睹这些系列，还是想更近距离地一睹其风采，现在都请加入我们的行列，让我们放大一些令人叹为观止的细节--<strong>技术和材料</strong>--它们在展会上吸引了众多兴奋的与会者的目光。  </p>','html-html-c4cfc39'=>'<iframe width="328" height="583" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VarxO-iOI_s" title="手镯 | D 系列 | 不分性别" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>','html-html-ce1d72c'=>'<iframe width="328" height="583" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S8QxWZkT5FA" title="钛金属 | 高级珠宝 | Eji Official" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>','title-heading-3c682f8'=>'锁的秘密','title-heading-6025d78'=>'完美的钛统治','title-headin